	{
	  "id": "ancient-battlefield",
	  "name": "古战场的记忆",
	  "category": "world",
	  "location": "古战场",
	  "one_shot": false,
	  "priority": 90,
	  "layers": [
		{
		  "level": "shallow",
		  "name": "目睹幻影",
		  "locks": [],
		  "effects": [
			{ "type": "message", "text": "暮色笼罩着古战场。残破的旗帜在风中轻响，似乎还能听见千年前的号角。", "position": "top", "auto_hide": 4 },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "你看到一个半透明的身影从废墟中走出，手持断剑，望向远方。那不是敌人——是一个倒在战场上的战士。", "position": "middle", "auto_hide": 5 },
			{ "type": "set_flag", "flag": "event:ancient-battlefield:shallow_seen" }
		  ]
		},
		{
		  "level": "middle",
		  "name": "触摸记忆",
		  "one_shot": true,
		  "locks": ["companion"],
		  "conditions": { "min_cycle": 2, "flag_set": "event:ancient-battlefield:shallow_seen" },
		  "effects": [
			{ "type": "message", "text": "你的同伴停下脚步，神情凝重。她也看到了那些幻影——不是幽灵，是这个世界不愿遗忘的东西。", "position": "top", "auto_hide": 4 },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "你伸出手，触碰了那道幻影。一瞬间，痛苦、恐惧、忠诚、遗憾——千万人的情感涌进你的意识。", "position": "middle", "auto_hide": 5 },
			{ "type": "set_flag", "flag": "event:ancient-battlefield:middle_done" },
			{ "type": "status", "text": "[color=yellow]你触碰了古战场的记忆...[/color]" }
		  ]
		},
		{
		  "level": "deep",
		  "name": "理解真相",
		  "one_shot": true,
		  "locks": ["fragment", "prerequisite"],
		  "conditions": {
			"min_cycle": 3,
			"flag_set": "event:ancient-battlefield:middle_done",
			"min_favor": { "companion": "静", "value": 30 }
		  },
		  "effects": [
			{ "type": "dialogue", "speaker": "静", "text": "这片战场埋葬的不是敌人。双方都是同一片土地上的人——被魔粒的诱惑分裂了。", "position": "center" },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "幻影汇聚成一片光幕。你看到了真相：这不是外敌入侵的战场，而是兄弟姐妹之间的内战。魔粒放大了人心中的裂痕。", "position": "middle", "auto_hide": 5 },
			{ "type": "set_flag", "flag": "event:ancient-battlefield:deep_done" },
			{ "type": "set_account_flag", "flag": "lore:ancient_civil_war" },
			{ "type": "status", "text": "[color=green]你理解了古战场的真相。[/color]" }
		  ]
		}
	  ]
	},

	{
	  "id": "crystal-cave",
	  "name": "结晶的真相",
	  "category": "world",
	  "location": "结晶洞穴",
	  "one_shot": false,
	  "priority": 90,
	  "layers": [
		{
		  "level": "shallow",
		  "name": "晶石的低语",
		  "locks": [],
		  "effects": [
			{ "type": "message", "text": "洞穴深处，晶石发出柔和的蓝光。走近一看，光芒中竟然隐约流动着文字般的纹路。", "position": "top", "auto_hide": 4 },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "这些晶石在记录什么——像是这个世界的历史，被封存在矿物的记忆里。", "position": "middle", "auto_hide": 4 },
			{ "type": "set_flag", "flag": "event:crystal-cave:shallow_seen" }
		  ]
		},
		{
		  "level": "middle",
		  "name": "魔法共鸣",
		  "one_shot": true,
		  "locks": ["companion"],
		  "conditions": { "min_cycle": 2, "flag_set": "event:crystal-cave:shallow_seen" },
		  "effects": [
			{ "type": "message", "text": "你触碰了一块发光的晶石。霎时间，魔法共鸣穿透了你的身体——你的意识被拉进了另一段时空。", "position": "top", "auto_hide": 5 },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "你看到了旧时代的末日：天空被撕裂，大地喷涌出黑雾。人们没有逃跑——他们在唱歌。", "position": "middle", "auto_hide": 5 },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "歌声中，晶石从地面生长出来，封存了最后的记忆。这不是灾难的记录，是遗言。", "position": "bottom", "auto_hide": 5 },
			{ "type": "set_flag", "flag": "event:crystal-cave:middle_done" },
			{ "type": "status", "text": "[color=yellow]晶石向你展示了旧时代的终结...[/color]" }
		  ]
		},
		{
		  "level": "deep",
		  "name": "选择的真相",
		  "one_shot": true,
		  "locks": ["fragment", "prerequisite"],
		  "conditions": {
			"min_cycle": 3,
			"flag_set": "event:crystal-cave:middle_done",
			"min_favor": { "companion": "塞拉菲娜", "value": 40 }
		  },
		  "effects": [
			{ "type": "dialogue", "speaker": "塞拉菲娜", "text": "你看到了吗？魔粒不是从天而降的灾难...是那个时代的人们主动召唤来的。", "position": "center" },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "最后的晶石打开了一扇光门。门后是一片纯白的空间——旧时代的学者们聚集在那里，做出了改变一切的决定。", "position": "middle", "auto_hide": 5 },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "魔粒不是污染。它是旧人类用来对抗某种更古老威胁的武器。他们选择了这种力量，尽管知道代价。", "position": "middle", "auto_hide": 5 },
			{ "type": "set_flag", "flag": "event:crystal-cave:deep_done" },
			{ "type": "set_account_flag", "flag": "lore:mana_particles_truth" },
			{ "type": "status", "text": "[color=green]你理解了魔粒的真正起源。[/color]" }
		  ]
		}
	  ]
	},

	{
	  "id": "tower-memory",
	  "name": "塔顶的星空",
