	  "location": "忘却之塔",
	  "one_shot": false,
	  "priority": 90,
	  "layers": [
		{
		  "level": "shallow",
		  "name": "相同的符文",
		  "locks": [],
		  "effects": [
			{ "type": "message", "text": "你抬头望向塔身——上面刻满了密密麻麻的符文。这些符号和神殿墙壁上的图案一模一样。", "position": "top", "auto_hide": 4 },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "塔和神殿之间有什么联系？这座塔似乎比神殿更古老。", "position": "middle", "auto_hide": 4 },
			{ "type": "set_flag", "flag": "event:tower-memory:shallow_seen" }
		  ]
		},
		{
		  "level": "middle",
		  "name": "古老的守护者",
		  "one_shot": true,
		  "locks": ["companion"],
		  "conditions": { "min_cycle": 2, "flag_set": "event:tower-memory:shallow_seen" },
		  "effects": [
			{ "type": "message", "text": "你踏上塔的阶梯。每走一步，空气中的魔力就浓重一分。在你接近塔顶时，一道光纹浮现——一个由符文构成的守卫拦住了去路。", "position": "top", "auto_hide": 5 },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "它不是敌人。它在等待——等待能读懂符文的人。", "position": "middle", "auto_hide": 4 },
			{ "type": "combat", "enemy": "res://scenes/characters/base_mob.tscn" },
			{ "type": "set_flag", "flag": "event:tower-memory:middle_done" },
			{ "type": "status", "text": "[color=yellow]击败了符文守卫。塔顶的路开放了。[/color]" }
		  ]
		},
		{
		  "level": "deep",
		  "name": "星图的秘密",
		  "one_shot": true,
		  "locks": ["fragment", "prerequisite"],
		  "conditions": {
			"min_cycle": 3,
			"flag_set": "event:tower-memory:middle_done",
			"companion_in_party": "阿斯特",
			"min_favor": { "companion": "阿斯特", "value": 30 }
		  },
		  "effects": [
			{ "type": "dialogue", "speaker": "阿斯特", "text": "这张星图...天哪，我看明白了。神殿不是起点——神殿是终点。所有的路都通向神殿，因为神殿是旧世界最后建造的东西。", "position": "center" },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "塔顶的穹顶上绘制着完整的星图。阿斯特指着其中一颗星——那是神殿的位置。所有符文路线都汇聚于一点。", "position": "middle", "auto_hide": 5 },
			{ "type": "message", "text": "神殿不是起源，是旧人类留给未来的最后一个信标。他们把所有知识都封存在那里，等待能破解循环的人。", "position": "middle", "auto_hide": 5 },
			{ "type": "set_flag", "flag": "event:tower-memory:deep_done" },
			{ "type": "set_account_flag", "flag": "lore:shrine_is_endpoint" },
			{ "type": "status", "text": "[color=green]阿斯特解读了星图——神殿是终点，不是起点。[/color]" }
		  ]
		}
	  ]
